| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-5923 — Recovery Inhibition (hunters)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 35b8f929-f865-5696-bfe9-961d0d8b2519"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
